## 5. Localization (i18n) & Sub-Systems

- **Dynamic UI Dictionary Mapping:** A custom React Hook ([useTranslation](file:///c:/Users/Abinaya/OneDrive/Desktop/smoking_habit_tracker/frontend/src/utils/i18n.js#133-146)) intercepts all static strings in the application and bridges them to a dictionary hashmap depending on the Zustand persistent store language variable.
- **AI-Level Translation Engineering:** If the "Tamil" language preference is detected on the frontend, the Python backend intercepts the Gemini Prompt payload and injects a "CRITICAL INSTRUCTION" to force the LLM to output its native intelligence wholly formulated in Tamil unicode script, bypassing standard translation APIs for much more native dialect reasoning.
